1
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:44,170
[My Bargain Queen]

2
00:01:44,170 --> 00:01:47,950
[Episode 6]

3
00:01:48,660 --> 00:01:51,110
Manager Sun didn't recommend me at all.

4
00:01:51,110 --> 00:01:53,120
Then, why did Sheng Zhening say that?

5
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:55,260
Sheng Zhening is the GM of Evergreen.

6
00:01:55,260 --> 00:01:58,890
He wants to give you the order, but couldn't say it directly because he wants to look good.

7
00:01:58,890 --> 00:02:01,910
That's why he used Manager Sun as an excuse.

8
00:02:04,440 --> 00:02:09,240
Then, why did he insist on giving the car purchasing project to me?

9
00:02:09,240 --> 00:02:14,710
It must be that he's done something wrong and he wants to make it up to you because he feels guilty.

10
00:02:14,710 --> 00:02:15,810
Why?

11
00:02:15,810 --> 00:02:17,500
What's with the heart?

12
00:02:17,500 --> 00:02:21,730
No no. I was just saying that if we see it this way, GM Sheng

13
00:02:21,730 --> 00:02:24,510
is not a bad person. Right?

14
00:02:26,890 --> 00:02:29,570
The water is too hot to drink.

15
00:02:30,570 --> 00:02:32,710
What is it? Is it yours?

16
00:02:34,130 --> 00:02:35,700
It's canned cat food.

17
00:02:35,700 --> 00:02:38,310
You don't have any cats. Why did you buy canned cat food then?

18
00:02:38,310 --> 00:02:39,870
I found a stray cat

19
00:02:39,870 --> 00:02:42,260
at Evergreen. I pity it,

20
00:02:42,260 --> 00:02:44,260
so I feed it sometimes.

21
00:02:45,040 --> 00:02:49,850
That's why you didn't quit. You will miss the cat too much.

22
00:02:51,230 --> 00:02:52,790
Sort of.

23
00:02:52,790 --> 00:02:55,070
It must be a cute cat.

24
00:02:55,070 --> 00:02:56,790
Super cute.

25
00:03:38,830 --> 00:03:41,280
Done! Beautiful! Here!

26
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:43,120
Let's change to another pose. Come.

27
00:03:43,120 --> 00:03:45,650
Another pose. The girl, swing your fist.

28
00:03:45,650 --> 00:03:46,880
The guy, you jump up.

29
00:03:46,880 --> 00:03:48,130
We want that pose.

30
00:03:48,130 --> 00:03:49,320
Come! Okay, okay.

31
00:03:49,320 --> 00:03:50,320
I will count to three.

32
00:03:50,320 --> 00:03:52,830
One, two, three. Action!

33
00:03:52,830 --> 00:03:55,290
Beautiful! Let's do it again!

34
00:03:55,290 --> 00:03:56,410
Very good!

35
00:03:56,410 --> 00:03:58,900
One, two, three.

36
00:04:17,710 --> 00:04:20,570
The set of photos I just took was perfect, very pretty.

37
00:04:20,570 --> 00:04:22,380
Let's change to another pose.

38
00:04:22,380 --> 00:04:23,650
How about carrying you like a princess?

39
00:04:23,650 --> 00:04:27,440
No, no, no. My hubby just hurt his arm, let's change to another pose—

40
00:04:27,440 --> 00:04:29,890
- Your arm!
- I'm fine.

41
00:04:29,890 --> 00:04:32,370
Very good!

42
00:04:32,370 --> 00:04:34,340
Beautiful! Come.

43
00:04:34,340 --> 00:04:35,290
Let's do another set!

44
00:04:35,290 --> 00:04:37,390
Keep the pose!

45
00:05:08,020 --> 00:05:12,190
You are just dropping off the contract, why did you dress so formally?

46
00:05:12,190 --> 00:05:14,210
I'm always like this, aren't I?

47
00:05:14,210 --> 00:05:16,940
Other than dropping off the contract,

48
00:05:16,940 --> 00:05:19,900
I want to thank Sheng Zhening in person today.

49
00:05:20,520 --> 00:05:23,570
He gave us such big business after all.

50
00:05:23,570 --> 00:05:26,360
Evergreen is the best client I've ever seen.

51
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:30,290
The job is good, they don't have many issues, and they pay fast.

52
00:05:30,290 --> 00:05:32,430
Go quickly. Good luck.

53
00:05:32,430 --> 00:05:33,970
Bye.

54
00:05:36,380 --> 00:05:38,910
Especially when they pay fast.

55
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:09,530
Miss Xia? Are you looking for GM Sheng?

56
00:06:09,530 --> 00:06:11,450
I'm here to drop off the contract for the car bulk buying.

57
00:06:11,450 --> 00:06:13,500
GM Sheng is not here. He's out.

58
00:06:13,500 --> 00:06:14,940
When is he coming back?

59
00:06:14,940 --> 00:06:19,510
I don't know when exactly, but if you have something urgent, I can give him a call to ask.

60
00:06:19,510 --> 00:06:22,310
There's no need for that. How about this?

61
00:06:22,310 --> 00:06:25,010
I will give you the contract, and you can pass it to him.

62
00:06:25,010 --> 00:06:27,870
- Okay.
- I'll get going then. Thank you.

63
00:06:57,310 --> 00:06:59,120
Long time no see!

64
00:07:04,950 --> 00:07:09,420
I was going to ask you if you got the handkerchief I left here for you last time.

65
00:07:11,170 --> 00:07:13,780
Aren't you going to ask why I'm here today?

66
00:07:15,570 --> 00:07:19,070
I'm here to give the contract to GM Sheng.

67
00:07:19,070 --> 00:07:22,180
But he's not here, it's not meant to be.

68
00:07:23,540 --> 00:07:26,330
You've been at Evergreen for such a long time.

69
00:07:26,330 --> 00:07:29,300
How do you feel about GM Sheng?

70
00:07:31,840 --> 00:07:33,980
You have a lot to say, don't you?

71
00:07:33,980 --> 00:07:37,010
Let me give you a piece of paper. Write down everything

72
00:07:37,010 --> 00:07:39,370
you want to say, rant, or complain.

73
00:07:39,990 --> 00:07:41,780
Don't be scared.

74
00:07:53,930 --> 00:07:55,120
What is it?
[Handsome, and overall he's okay!]

75
00:07:55,120 --> 00:07:56,850
[Handsome, and overall he's okay!]

76
00:07:56,850 --> 00:07:58,450
"Handsome"?

77
00:08:00,820 --> 00:08:03,600
"Overall he's okay."

78
00:08:04,140 --> 00:08:06,710
Is he okay? I don't think so.

79
00:08:06,710 --> 00:08:09,760
He's so weird. He has OCD.

80
00:08:09,760 --> 00:08:13,550
He likes to nitpick everything and always has problems.

81
00:08:13,550 --> 00:08:17,280
And he's so petty and unreasonable.

82
00:08:17,900 --> 00:08:19,690
Forget it.

83
00:08:20,410 --> 00:08:22,540
I was only talking about a part of him.

84
00:08:22,540 --> 00:08:25,890
But he's a good person overall.

85
00:08:26,400 --> 00:08:27,980
I'm here to thank him

86
00:08:27,980 --> 00:08:30,550
today.

87
00:08:31,580 --> 00:08:33,900
We had some conflicts before,

88
00:08:33,900 --> 00:08:36,780
and he still helped me despite those conflicts.

89
00:08:36,780 --> 00:08:38,570
I really want to thank him.

90
00:08:38,570 --> 00:08:41,270
But he's not here. What else can I do? It's not meant to be.

91
00:08:41,270 --> 00:08:44,050
I wonder when I am going to see him.

92
00:08:44,050 --> 00:08:47,300
I just hope that everything

93
00:08:47,300 --> 00:08:49,280
goes well for GM Sheng.

94
00:08:49,280 --> 00:08:51,890
Healthy and happy every day.

95
00:08:55,270 --> 00:08:59,290
You work so hard, too. I also wish everything goes well with you, wish you happiness and health.

96
00:08:59,290 --> 00:09:01,530
Okay? I'm leaving.

97
00:09:03,030 --> 00:09:04,670
Do your thing.

98
00:09:06,010 --> 00:09:07,890
You want to write some more?

99
00:09:26,990 --> 00:09:29,120
GM Sheng should be here soon.

100
00:09:29,120 --> 00:09:30,730
He comes to check out the flowers

101
00:09:30,730 --> 00:09:33,960
here every day at this time. Please wait.

102
00:09:33,960 --> 00:09:35,560
Really?

103
00:09:38,270 --> 00:09:41,070
Okay. I will wait for him.

104
00:10:10,970 --> 00:10:12,530
You are here.

105
00:10:14,430 --> 00:10:15,930
Brother Hebo.

106
00:10:15,930 --> 00:10:18,260
I think you aren't as good to me as before.

107
00:10:18,260 --> 00:10:20,260
I haven't heard from you for days.

108
00:10:20,260 --> 00:10:22,420
You've wrongly accused me.

109
00:10:22,420 --> 00:10:26,460
I've been on a business trip, but I've been thinking about you.

110
00:10:26,460 --> 00:10:27,990
Please, sit.

111
00:10:29,410 --> 00:10:31,730
I asked you to be here today,

112
00:10:31,730 --> 00:10:34,240
so I can give you your wedding gift.

113
00:10:34,240 --> 00:10:36,190
What is it? Let me see.

114
00:10:36,190 --> 00:10:38,480
Open it and take a look.

115
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:41,830
I found a designer to customize it for you.

116
00:10:41,830 --> 00:10:44,310
Wow, it's so pretty!

117
00:10:45,110 --> 00:10:46,380
Do you like it?

118
00:10:46,380 --> 00:10:47,880
I love it!

119
00:10:47,880 --> 00:10:50,710
I must wear it at my wedding.

120
00:10:51,630 --> 00:10:54,420
So pretty.

121
00:10:56,210 --> 00:10:58,790
Brother Hebo,

122
00:10:58,790 --> 00:11:02,330
I want you and my brother together to hold each of my arms

123
00:11:02,330 --> 00:11:05,460
and hand me to Zhijuan.

124
00:11:05,460 --> 00:11:08,030
I can't do that, your brother will be jealous.

125
00:11:08,030 --> 00:11:11,320
He won't! He would want it, too.

126
00:11:11,320 --> 00:11:15,630
If you didn't donate your blood to me after the car accident,

127
00:11:15,630 --> 00:11:18,500
I wouldn't be here right now.

128
00:11:19,990 --> 00:11:22,470
I know it's a gesture from you and your brother,

129
00:11:22,470 --> 00:11:24,930
but it's not how it should work.

130
00:11:24,930 --> 00:11:27,030
- But I...
- Be good.

131
00:11:27,030 --> 00:11:29,350
Even though I can't hold your arm,

132
00:11:29,350 --> 00:11:33,240
I will be there to witness the happy moment.

133
00:11:34,970 --> 00:11:37,160
Okay then.

134
00:11:40,290 --> 00:11:43,960
Where are you going in such a hurry, GM Sheng?

135
00:12:12,640 --> 00:12:14,840
What a coincidence. What are you doing here?

136
00:12:14,840 --> 00:12:18,250
What a coincidence! Great.

137
00:12:18,250 --> 00:12:22,400
I wanted to tell you that the car bulk-buying case is over.

138
00:12:23,260 --> 00:12:25,810
I was just talking to your gardener.

139
00:12:25,810 --> 00:12:27,610
He was praising you.

140
00:12:27,610 --> 00:12:30,310
- What did he say?
- Handsome.

141
00:12:30,310 --> 00:12:33,860
There's more. He said you are okay.

142
00:12:33,860 --> 00:12:35,130
That's it?

143
00:12:35,130 --> 00:12:37,330
What else do you want?

144
00:12:38,730 --> 00:12:41,200
I've told you last time,

145
00:12:41,200 --> 00:12:45,600
the juice of blue Morning Glory is poisonous. You will get a skin allergy.

146
00:12:49,010 --> 00:12:52,240
Wipe your wound with it.

147
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:55,010
The juice of blue Morning Glory is poisonous.

148
00:12:55,010 --> 00:12:57,760
You might suffer from a skin allergy if you leave the juice on the skin.

149
00:12:57,760 --> 00:12:59,910
Last time?

150
00:13:00,490 --> 00:13:04,450
Which time? Why don't I remember you telling me that?

151
00:13:04,450 --> 00:13:06,070
Stop pretending.

152
00:13:06,070 --> 00:13:09,600
Your disguise is gone.

153
00:13:15,760 --> 00:13:18,170
When?

154
00:13:18,170 --> 00:13:20,420
Not too long ago.

155
00:13:20,420 --> 00:13:21,920
Then when was that?

156
00:13:21,920 --> 00:13:24,460
When I was on the business trip with you.

157
00:13:24,460 --> 00:13:27,150
I saw the handkerchief in your room.

158
00:13:27,150 --> 00:13:29,690
I then realized that you were the gardener.

159
00:13:30,550 --> 00:13:33,410
Wipe your hands. Really, you'll get allergies.

160
00:13:36,890 --> 00:13:38,920
Thank you.

161
00:13:38,920 --> 00:13:41,100
I look forward to meeting you next time.

162
00:13:41,100 --> 00:13:46,050
I'm not finished. I actually want to thank you.

163
00:13:46,050 --> 00:13:49,210
I want to thank you for comforting me here that day.

164
00:13:50,280 --> 00:13:51,620
That's it.

165
00:13:51,620 --> 00:13:55,980
I've told the rest to the gardener. You don't have to know it.

166
00:14:06,980 --> 00:14:10,280
Compensate for seven days...

167
00:14:10,280 --> 00:14:12,020
I'm back.

168
00:14:12,020 --> 00:14:15,430
Sister Qian, did you win the lottery? You look really happy.

169
00:14:15,430 --> 00:14:16,650
I'm fine.

170
00:14:16,650 --> 00:14:19,690
Didn't you say that you hate going to Evergreen the most?

171
00:14:20,430 --> 00:14:24,750
I just realized that Sheng Zhening is not that annoying.

172
00:14:24,750 --> 00:14:27,130
Huh?

173
00:14:27,130 --> 00:14:29,000
How could you not find him annoying?

174
00:14:29,000 --> 00:14:32,000
I... I can't put it in one sentence.

175
00:14:32,000 --> 00:14:33,830
I'm going in.

176
00:14:35,390 --> 00:14:37,220
[Worth or Not]

177
00:14:46,050 --> 00:14:48,720
What's wrong with you? Are you not happy?

178
00:14:48,720 --> 00:14:53,500
Why do I feel like Sheng Zhening is getting closer to Sister Qian?

179
00:14:53,500 --> 00:14:56,160
How's that any of your business?

180
00:14:56,160 --> 00:14:58,830
How is it not my business?

181
00:15:01,570 --> 00:15:04,490
Stop moving. Hold your face.

182
00:15:06,280 --> 00:15:09,760
Don't tell me that you like Sister Qian.

183
00:15:11,150 --> 00:15:13,920
What's going on, Mu Xiaoyan?

184
00:15:13,920 --> 00:15:16,090
Mu Xiaoyan?

185
00:15:16,090 --> 00:15:19,920
That's right! I do like her.

186
00:15:19,920 --> 00:15:22,320
- Really?
- Really.

187
00:15:22,320 --> 00:15:24,610
Actually, I've been having a crush on her since college.

188
00:15:24,610 --> 00:15:28,250
But she was with He Zhijuan, I couldn't say anything.

189
00:15:28,250 --> 00:15:32,350
Until now, I still like her very much.

190
00:15:34,190 --> 00:15:38,170
That's not right. You've been having a crush on her for so long and I've been with you guys all along.

191
00:15:38,170 --> 00:15:40,310
Someone as intuitive as I am,

192
00:15:40,310 --> 00:15:43,400
I didn't even notice it.

193
00:15:43,400 --> 00:15:46,370
I got it. No, I'm not shutting up.

194
00:15:47,180 --> 00:15:50,760
Okay, I won't say a word. I promise.

195
00:16:09,540 --> 00:16:13,820
- Hubby, put it here. Is it hot?
- It's fine.

196
00:16:13,820 --> 00:16:16,900
Why couldn't we just buy ready-made ones?

197
00:16:16,900 --> 00:16:21,720
That wouldn't work. I have to make the wedding favors myself.

198
00:16:21,720 --> 00:16:23,520
Give me the gift bag.

199
00:16:23,520 --> 00:16:25,560
- This one?
- Yeah.

200
00:16:35,920 --> 00:16:38,530
- Wait! This one is no good.
- What?

201
00:16:38,530 --> 00:16:40,400
This one has flaws.

202
00:16:40,400 --> 00:16:43,590
Look, the pattern is not clear.

203
00:16:43,590 --> 00:16:46,320
If you didn't point it out, I wouldn't have noticed.

204
00:16:46,320 --> 00:16:50,720
I want everything to be perfect for our wedding.

205
00:16:50,720 --> 00:16:53,880
You can have this one.

206
00:16:55,740 --> 00:16:58,490
- Is it good?
- Yes.

207
00:16:58,490 --> 00:17:02,530
Hubby, the wedding rehearsal is tomorrow.

208
00:17:02,530 --> 00:17:05,000
Are you ready?

209
00:17:05,900 --> 00:17:07,920
Don't worry.

210
00:17:09,290 --> 00:17:12,640
I want one, too. You feed me.

211
00:17:21,290 --> 00:17:23,560
Is it good?

212
00:17:27,340 --> 00:17:30,390
Why are you still here? I thought you'd finished your mission.

213
00:17:30,390 --> 00:17:32,730
I still have two days before getting paid.

214
00:17:32,730 --> 00:17:34,750
After getting my money, I'll leave.

215
00:17:34,750 --> 00:17:37,560
So I am holding fast to my last shift.

216
00:17:38,650 --> 00:17:40,710
What are you doing here?

217
00:17:41,370 --> 00:17:43,030
Playing with the cat.

218
00:17:44,130 --> 00:17:46,930
I was afraid that it didn't have enough food last night, so I came to check on it.

219
00:17:46,930 --> 00:17:49,230
I've already fed it.

220
00:17:50,290 --> 00:17:53,070
Don't always feed it this nice canned food.

221
00:17:53,070 --> 00:17:57,060
If it gets picky, what am I going to feed it after you leave?

222
00:17:57,060 --> 00:18:00,570
It's so small and still growing. It has to eat good food.

223
00:18:00,570 --> 00:18:01,590
Also,

224
00:18:01,590 --> 00:18:06,010
even if I leave, I will still come back to feed it something nice.

225
00:18:07,680 --> 00:18:09,770
You said it.

226
00:18:10,780 --> 00:18:13,380
Then I should thank you for it.

227
00:18:14,850 --> 00:18:18,890
It loves the food I feed, right?

228
00:18:21,760 --> 00:18:24,210
Are you doing anything tonight?

229
00:18:24,660 --> 00:18:26,650
I will take you out to dinner.

230
00:18:26,650 --> 00:18:29,590
Why are you treating me to dinner all of a sudden?

231
00:18:29,590 --> 00:18:31,920
Because you treat it.

232
00:18:32,570 --> 00:18:34,790
I don't eat cat food.

233
00:18:34,790 --> 00:18:37,950
Don't worry. Cat food is too expensive for you.

234
00:18:37,950 --> 00:18:39,760
I'm still growing.

235
00:18:39,760 --> 00:18:43,380
I can't have food that is too cheap.

236
00:18:44,170 --> 00:18:46,810
- Have this.
- Me?

237
00:18:52,990 --> 00:18:55,030
Let's sit there.

238
00:18:55,030 --> 00:18:56,950
Here.

239
00:19:01,030 --> 00:19:02,690
Hello, would you like to order now?

240
00:19:02,690 --> 00:19:06,240
- We need to take a look at the menu first. We'll ask for you later.
- Okay.

241
00:19:07,630 --> 00:19:11,320
It's so expensive here. Don't you know how expensive this place is, when you work at Evergreen?

242
00:19:11,320 --> 00:19:16,690
I know, but it's okay to treat myself sometimes.

243
00:19:16,690 --> 00:19:19,870
- But...
- You take a look.

244
00:19:19,870 --> 00:19:21,940
I'm going to the restroom.

245
00:19:25,530 --> 00:19:27,790
So expensive.

246
00:19:28,930 --> 00:19:31,390
Don't tell me he is going to dine and dash!

247
00:19:34,260 --> 00:19:35,520
Vice GM Qin.

248
00:19:35,520 --> 00:19:38,340
When we are getting the check at the end, you say

249
00:19:38,340 --> 00:19:41,290
"GM Qin has paid for the dinner. Just sign here."

250
00:19:41,290 --> 00:19:43,310
- Okay.
- Okay.

251
00:19:48,430 --> 00:19:51,130
Would you like to order, Miss?

252
00:19:51,130 --> 00:19:54,890
I... I would like a stir-fried vegetable.

253
00:19:54,890 --> 00:19:59,780
A... spinach with nuts.

254
00:19:59,780 --> 00:20:01,880
- Do you have a half order of Yangzhou fried rice?
- No.

255
00:20:01,880 --> 00:20:03,890
Let's get a Yangzhou fried rice and that's enough!

256
00:20:03,890 --> 00:20:05,520
Okay. Here's what you've ordered,

257
00:20:05,520 --> 00:20:09,530
Spinach with nuts, stir-fried vegetables, and Yangzhou fried rice.

258
00:20:09,530 --> 00:20:11,610
That's enough. That's all.

259
00:20:11,610 --> 00:20:13,760
- That's it?
- It's enough.

260
00:20:13,760 --> 00:20:16,500
I'm trying to lose weight recently.

261
00:20:16,500 --> 00:20:19,640
You need to eat to have enough energy to lose weight.

262
00:20:19,640 --> 00:20:22,920
Let me order a couple of dishes more.

263
00:20:22,920 --> 00:20:26,940
I want to add a stir-fried nagaimo and fungus.
