264
00:20:26,940 --> 00:20:29,700
Stir fried abalone with XO sauce.

265
00:20:29,700 --> 00:20:32,130
Are you sure?

266
00:20:33,410 --> 00:20:35,820
Crispy prawns with salted egg sauce.

267
00:20:38,720 --> 00:20:40,380
Baked ribs with wasabi and red wine.

268
00:20:40,380 --> 00:20:42,450
That's enough. We can't finish this much.

269
00:20:42,450 --> 00:20:44,300
Let's get a couple more, a couple more.

270
00:20:44,300 --> 00:20:46,830
Baby Chinese broccoli with ginger sauce.

271
00:20:46,830 --> 00:20:50,290
And lastly, Dalian fresh scallops with black truffle.
